{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend the \u00a3650 cost of living payments to contributions-based ESA claimants",
        "additional_details": "We believe it is unjust for people claiming ESA on the basis of their NI contributions to be excluded from these payments.\r\n\r\nThe disabled and sick often use a larger proportion of their income on essential bills, and anyone receiving contribution-based ESA should receive the \u00a3650 cost of living payment.",
        "background": "There are people who are on contributions-based benefits who cannot get the \u00a3650 cost of living payment because they are not on any Income Related Benefit.",
